	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Can somebody direct me to a good EPROM writer?  I also need an EPROM eraser.  The reason I want this is so that I can write my SMB Hack to CHR and PRG chips that I took from a SMB cartridge, then put them back into the cartridge, so that I can play my hack with an actual NES.  
<br />
<br />Please, somebody, just point me in the right direction.
<br />
<br />Thanks in advance.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
